quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  28,14,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko ngun, o fotondi- ri, Min ngokki mo faamu e ganndal. Ko wano non Min njo…ďirta mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen."
  28,15,"O naatiri e saare nden, feewndo welsindaare yim…ďe mayre; o tawi wor…ďe …ói…óo no ha…ďa ton: go…ó…óo on ko jiyaa…óo e le√Īol makko, oya on ko jiyaa…óo e ay…ďe makko …ďen. Jeyaa…óo e le√Īol makko ngol …óa…ď…ďiri faabo e hoore jiyaa…óo e ga√Īo makko on. Muusaa uttii mo, nde gayni fii makko. [Muusaa] maaki: "∆äum …óoo, ko jiyaa…óum e kuu…óe seytaane. Pellet, ko o ga√Īo, majjinoowo …ďanngu…óo"."
  28,16,"O maaki: "Joomi am, mi too√Īii hoore-am; haforanam." O haforani mo. Pellet, ko KaŇčko woni Haforoowo, jurmotoo…óo On."
  28,17,"O maaki: "Joomi am, sabu ko neemin…óaa ko e am, mi wonataa ballo bom…ďe …ďe"."
  28,18,"O wonti kul…óo ka saare, homo habbii [nanngeede]. Tawi faabinornoo…óo mo on hanki, homo faabinora mo [hannde kadi]. Muusaa maakani mo: "Pellet, ko a bew…óo …ďanngu…óo"."
  28,19,"Nde Muusaa faandinoo nanngugol taw…óo on ko ga√Īo ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo, o wi'i: "ey ma yo Muusaa, a faala bargol lam, wano ittirno…óaa woŇčkii non haŇčki? A faandaaki, si wonaa wonugol dunndarankeejo ka leydi, a faandaaki jeyeede e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen"."
  28,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ďuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, homo yaccoo, o wi'i: "eey ma Muusaa, mbatu ngun no fewjana fii bargol maa. Yaltu (e leydi ndin). Ko mi jiyaa…óo e laa…ďanoo…ďe ma"."
  28,21,"O yalti ton, ko o kul…óo, himo tijjii [nanngeede]. O maaki: "Joomi am, dan…óndam e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen"."